# MISSION: PHASE 01 - SYNC HARDENING (RETRY)
## Technical Mission
Resolve the silent failures in the 1xBet sync.
1. Implement `scripts/lib/auth-validator.mjs`.
2. Use a direct `fetch` to verify the cookie.
3. If `process.env.BETHISTORY_COOKIE` is missing, you MUST log "ENVIRONMENT_SECRET_MISSING" and exit.
4. Integrate this into `scripts/sync-bet-history.mjs`.

## Deployment
Push to main and verify Vercel build.